"Include the :option:`--replSet <mongod --replSet>` option with the name "
"of the replica set as well as any other options specific to your "
"configuration, such as :option:`--dbpath <mongod --dbpath>` and "
":option:`--bind_ip <mongod --bind_ip>`."
msgstr ""

