"your configuration, such as ``--bind_ip``."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/tutorial/rotate-encryption-key.txt:135
#: ../source/tutorial/rotate-encryption-key.txt:181
msgid ""
"If using a configuration file, remove the "
":setting:`security.kmip.rotateMasterKey` setting."
msgstr ""

